::: Ra, Megatron, and Waspinator stop firing at each other and try to talk 
peacefully to the others. :::

::: Ra ::: Zues, my brother. In tims of war we much choose sides. Each of us 
are like country's with temporary alliences and enemies. I have signed a 
traty with Megatron and by doing so we I have ended my allience you you. I am 
sorry, but this is the way things must be.

::: He moves to reveal Megatron who chucks a grenade at Zues. Waspinator then 
points to the ceiling, blasts a hole in it, and the Predacons fly out taking 
numerous hits by the Autoguns. :::
